"{\"uid\": \"fansided.com-posts-uswnt-3-up-and-coming-stars-at-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The USWNT's future generation has arrived.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 42, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not on its way.\", \"from\": 43, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are looking at it.\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 85, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gone with the old, in with the new.\", \"from\": 87, \"to\": 122, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a key theme for Emma Hayes as she named eight players under the age of 26 to the roster for theParis Olympics.\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 148, \"end\": 158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Hayes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Hayes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With youth brings excitement as this group of players looks for a bounce back from last summer under new leadership.\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There were only two players under 26 at the 2020 Olympics under the guidance of Vlatko Andonovski.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vlatko_Andonovski\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vlatko Andonovski\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vlatko_Andonovski\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vlatko_Andonovski\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The page has turned.\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Time to click in those seatbelts - this group has a young core that is more than ready to bring this team back to life.\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are our three rising stars for the USWNT you need to keep an eye on at the Olympics this summer.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Note:Our criteria for 'up-and-coming': have to be 23 or younger and below the 45 cap threshold.)\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jenna Nighswonger, a native of Huntington Beach, California, has been truly exceptional since being drafted fourth overall in the 2023 NWSL Draft.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 803, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\", \"score\": 0.9999978688974778, \"rank\": 1.3097452666957783e-06, \"text\": \"Jenna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenna_Maroney\"}, {\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huntington Beach, California\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\"}, {\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huntington Beach, California\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similar to the reliability of Grandma's homemade cookies, she always delivers.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The former Florida State standout has consistently excelled in a position that once was relatively unfamiliar to her from the beginning of her career with NJ/NY Gotham FC.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1040, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_State_Seminoles_football\", \"score\": 0.995911323649949, \"rank\": 0.004071995634776042, \"text\": \"Florida State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_State_Seminoles_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida_State_Seminoles_football\"}, {\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NY_Gotham_FC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NJ/NY Gotham FC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NY_Gotham_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NY_Gotham_FC\"}, {\"begin\": 1184, \"end\": 1199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NY_Gotham_FC\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NJ/NY Gotham FC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NY_Gotham_FC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NY_Gotham_FC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2023 NWSL Rookie of the Year converted from a traditional central midfielder to a left-back just last season.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really hated left back at first,\\\" said Nighswonger on 'The Women's Game' podcast.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Then I just learned to embrace it and go with it.\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, I really truly love it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1482, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"THE LEFTY PUTS IT AWAY\\u00e2\\u009a\\u00bd\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008f\\u00f0\\u009f\\u008f\\u009f\\u00ef\\u00b8\\u008fJenna Nighswonger, scores her first ever senior international goal in the 86\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 minute just a few miles away from her hometown of Huntington Beach, California!\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huntington Beach, California\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\"}, {\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Huntington Beach, California\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huntington_Beach,_California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00f0\\u009f\\u008c\\u008aWhat a way to show up for a little hometown visit\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u008f\\u00f0\\u009f\\u008f\\u00bc  \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0091\\u008f\\u00f0\\u009f\\u008f\\u00bcpic.twitter.com/7WhIHLNBGy  The results in her new position with Gotham granted her a look on the national stage.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1863, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gotham_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0769306183590833e-20, \"text\": \"Gotham\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gotham_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gotham_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ever since that first call-up in November 2023, Nighswonger has made quite the impression.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those attacking instincts have not gone away.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That is what makes her such a dynamite wide defender.\", \"from\": 2001, \"to\": 2054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her willingness to bomb forward and execute that final cross is going to be incredibly useful at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2022 ACC women's soccer tournament MVP started in her first match for the Stars and Stripes a little over a month after that first call.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2176, \"end\": 2179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlantic_Coast_Conference\", \"score\": 0.9999999977449079, \"rank\": 2.2104892320859634e-09, \"text\": \"ACC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlantic_Coast_Conference\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlantic_Coast_Conference\"}, {\"begin\": 2206, \"end\": 2209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\", \"score\": 0.9999901215898237, \"rank\": 9.518708549086363e-06, \"text\": \"MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Most_valuable_player\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The USWNT's No.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2312, \"end\": 2317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"13 later netted her first goal in the 2024 CONCACAF W Gold Cup,a cool penaltyto put the United States up by four over the Dominican Republic.\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2412, \"end\": 2425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999831743, \"rank\": 1.6907837643300157e-11, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2446, \"end\": 2464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominican_Republic_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9847068713449424, \"rank\": 0.014985534198866404, \"text\": \"Dominican Republic\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominican_Republic_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dominican_Republic_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hayes was cautious in the final match before the team jetted off to France, sitting Nighswonger due to load management.\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2535, \"end\": 2541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2793835303371904e-13, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was likely a good call by the former Chelsea leader with the defender playing the second minutes on her club team this season.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2627, \"end\": 2634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9975278268615906, \"rank\": 0.002478299925103967, \"text\": \"Chelsea\", 