 \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shaw, who may be the second-best number 10 on this team, recorded seven goals and one assist in her first 14 appearances for the USWNT, including five goals in her first five starts.\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3150, \"end\": 3154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999988644959, \"rank\": 1.1349396160454658e-09, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}, {\"begin\": 3279, \"end\": 3284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though Hayes did not show much trust in Shaw in the send-off matches, her ability to flex into a winger or a false nine should allow her to see the pitch as an impact substitute when the time is right.\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3379, \"end\": 3383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999988644959, \"rank\": 1.1349396160454658e-09, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are few things Shaw can not do on the ball.\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3562, \"end\": 3566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999988644959, \"rank\": 1.1349396160454658e-09, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Threading the needle with a through ball?\", \"from\": 3591, \"to\": 3632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course, she can do that.\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Driving centrally for a strike with either foot?\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All day.\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3718, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On a club team that has not been very productive offensive this season, SD's No.\", \"from\": 3720, \"to\": 3800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"11 is tied for the team lead in goals with three.\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The beginning of her career with the Stars and Stripes has been one many dream of.\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The results we have seen in 2024 from Shaw do not lie.\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3972, \"end\": 3976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999988644959, \"rank\": 1.1349396160454658e-09, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics is her time to show world football what the coming years will look like.\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4074, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the summer of Trinity Rodman.\", \"from\": 4076, \"to\": 4113, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4098, \"end\": 4112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trinity Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With a starting role on one of the biggest stages under the guidance of a brilliant mind, her stardom could hit a whole new level.\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4244, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We could even make an argument that she is the USWNT's most important player as it searches for ways to find the back of the net.\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4292, \"end\": 4297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 22-year-old Washington Spirit winger has been brilliant in the NWSL this season, showing off just how deep her bag of tricks really is in the final third.\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4392, \"end\": 4409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.467271333774378e-46, \"text\": \"Washington Spirit\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_Spirit\"}, {\"begin\": 4443, \"end\": 4447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.049667128924589e-22, \"text\": \"NWSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Women's_Soccer_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you did not already know - that bag is deep just like one of those large-sized duffle bags you'd take on vacation.\", \"from\": 4535, \"to\": 4652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe even deeper.\", \"from\": 4653, \"to\": 4671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The California native is simply a walking highlight reel.\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4676, \"end\": 4686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9122998067190187, \"rank\": 0.09165837662852862, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You never know what kind of magic she is going to pull next.\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4790, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That unpredictability could be crucial in breaking the struggles in front of the net.\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tricky Trin at it again!pic.twitter.com/LLORYmDune  In the draw to Costa Rica, Rodman was awarded the 'Michelob Ultra Superior Woman of the Match' by U.S. Soccer for her play down the right flank.\", \"from\": 4878, \"to\": 5074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4945, \"end\": 4955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Costa_Rica_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6340720930922705, \"rank\": 0.5771077304207711, \"text\": \"Costa Rica\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Costa_Rica_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Costa_Rica_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4957, \"end\": 4963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\", \"score\": 0.9999973522065868, \"rank\": 2.633988648111959e-06, \"text\": \"Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dennis_Rodman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is tied with